questions.questions: Which German cities have more than 250000 inhabitants?
questions.originalQuery: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { { ?uri rdf:type dbo:City . } UNION { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Town . } ?uri dbo:country res:Germany . ?uri dbo:populationTotal ?population . FILTER ( ?population > 250000 ) }
